main: ^Welcome back gamers! Today we're going to be diving into an exciting world for an intense FPS with a twist- we're going... outside.
^Touching grass has never been my speciality but recently my backyard has been invaded by gnomes!
^Get ready to blast your way through perilous gnome hordes. It's all about quick reflexes, precision aiming, and tactical gameplay as we battle our way through gnome-infested terrain.
^Ive equipt my trusty rake in my LEFT TRIGGER and speedy SHIFT click running shoes.
^All we have to do for this first area is eliminate all the gnomes in the backyard. Once clear, we will live another day.
^Are you ready for some gnome-smashing fun? Let's dive in and show these little creatures who's boss!
